# Daily UI/UX Flow Optimization Process Handoff


## Introduction


This document outlines the process for handling the Daily UI/UX Flow Optimization task, following the handoff from FORGE. File "Daily_UI_UX_Flow_Optimization_1774193692719" has been moved to the Drive input folder for further action. The purpose of this document is to provide a structured guide for optimizing the UI/UX flows in alignment with Forgotten Formula PMA's healing mission and values.


## Objectives


- Enhance user experience with an intuitive, healing-centric interface
- Improve navigation efficiency for members accessing wellness approaches
- Ensure the digital environment reflects our identity as a healing mission focused on nature over synthetic
- Align interface flow with FFPMA's commitment to member sovereignty and privacy


